videos.description: Nahiem Alleyne gets pressured by Collin Gillespie in the corner and he drains the triple as Virginia Tech trails Villanova 56-54.
videos.headline: Alleyne eyes a 3-ball on Gillespie to cut Hokies' deficit

videos.description: Keve Aluma sinks the layup to put Virginia Tech up 63-62 over Villanova late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Aluma draws the crucial and-1 as Virginia Tech takes late lead over Nova) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aluma draws the crucial and-1 as Virginia Tech takes late lead over Nova

videos.description: Villanova's Justin Moore makes both free throws after Justyn Mutts is called for the foul, tying the game at 64-64 vs. Virginia Tech.
